{"tid":1540952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好野 贏了。放下心頭大石 ！ 多謝連登仔","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:21:50.000Z","uid":211724,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e5918cf6e91fa30d7ca8bcc537e61313ab714168","tid":1540952,"uid":211724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你班曱甴無人驚過呀！林奠要聽民意就一早聽咗啦！洗撚等到今日？<br />\n<br />\n美國國會9月復會，民主、共和兩黨都支持香港人，攬炒又帶埋啲英國人泥香港，林奠條八婆先肯「回應」一條！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但家下個個外國人連埋班無腦香港人都當香港人贏咗呀，無人知而家唔係「正式撤回」，只係「按議事規則動議撤回修例」！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港立法會10月先復會</span>，到時無晒班外國勢力，又唔夠票撤回唔到條條例，你班曱甴死撚晒都無人理呀！<br />\n<br />\n仲有，<span style=\"color: violet;\">你對唔對得住班手足</span>，你開心當贏既時候佢地仲面臨緊判刑㗎！仲有走咗嗰幾位呀！<br />\n<br />\n你班黑狗點都要還㗎啦，就快到你地！<br />\n<br />\n全部人繼續推爆條法案，做文宣，落街解釋一下比啲人聽清楚！！！<br />\n<br />\n總之<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">612</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">811</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">831</span>"},{"pid":"115a31c0b1d690295860778323077ee0f6c71f7c","tid":1540952,"uid":211724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"5d1a13de8ee3083c8e29bb04b3028e2d2af808b0","tid":1540952,"uid":317299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.